'''白鹿潭'''是位于[[韩国|韩国]][[济州岛|济州岛]][[汉拏山|汉拏山]]山顶火山口的湖泊，海拔1850米，湖面直径约300米，周长1公里，深约6米，是韩国最大的天然湖泊。<ref name="煤炭">{{cite web|url=http://www.sxcoal.com/gjms/752400/articlenew.html|title=韩国地理环境|publisher=国际煤炭网|accessdate=2014-11-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016045854/http://www.sxcoal.com/gjms/752400/articlenew.html|archivedate=2014-10-16}}</ref>

传说在很久以前，神仙们曾骑着白鹿来到[[汉拏山|汉拏山]]游玩。“白鹿潭”因此而得名。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.keyunzhan.com/jingdian-2052/ |title = 白鹿潭简介 |accessdate = 2014-11-03 |archive-date = 2020-04-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200417154420/https://www.keyunzhan.com/jingdian-2052/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

